## OUTPUT — WRITE HERE

Write the classification by invoking ``curator.sh builders`` via
execute_bash. Output target:

    {{ output_path }}

DO NOT use ``fs_write`` directly.

### 1. Initialize

    curator.sh builders init {{ output_path }} --schema classify

### 2. Set every required field in one call

    curator.sh builders add {{ output_path }} \
        --set quintet.media=<media> \
        --set quintet.form=<form> \
        --set quintet.register=<register> \
        --set quintet.discipline=<discipline> \
        --set quintet.audience=<audience> \
        --set topic='<3-12 word descriptor>' \
        --set reasoning='<2-4 sentences citing source evidence>'

All seven fields are required.
